processFile:
CDFACOPY PROCESS

    SNODE=DMNAT01

        &INFILE='%FA_FILE_FOUND'

        &FILENAME='%FA_NOT_PATH'

CDCP COPY

    FROM (

        FILE='&INFILE'

        PNODE

)

ckpt = 2M

    TO (

        FILE = '&FILENAME'

        SNODE

        DISP=RPL

                )

IF (CDCP EQ 0) THEN
DELFILE RUN TASK PNODE (PGM=Windows) SYSOPTS='CMD(del ~'&INFILE~')'
EIF

PEND
